764
00:50:52,466 --> 00:50:55,802
<i>Johnny Damon'a ödememiz gereken parayı
ona verdik.

765
00:50:55,970 --> 00:50:57,636
<i>Jeremy Giambi.</i>

766
00:50:57,804 --> 00:51:00,014
